we haven't had other complaints, so i wonder if that was a bad driver/RTC hardware in one particular device? if you can reproduce that, we should investigate, but for now i'll stick with the 1970-01-01 cutoff from the original code.

(do we have CTS tests for the minimum range that the system clock can support? seems like we ought to.)

